Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.05,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.55,Default,16,0,0,0,,零贰！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.47,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.26,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.22,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.52,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.36,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.78,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我能遇到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.86,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我超喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.37,Default,16,0,0,0,,零贰　我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.25,Default,16,0,0,0,,我超喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.92,Default,666,0,0,0,,笨蛋　把通讯断开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.59,Default,214,0,0,0,,是啊　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.30,Default,390,0,0,0,,真是两个笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.63,Default,15,0,0,0,,太好了　你们两个...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.72,Default,16,0,0,0,,零贰　那个穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.72,Default,16,0,0,0,,能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.27,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,当然啦　要是和 Darling 一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.81,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:47.12,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.38,Default,9a,0,0,0,,差不多是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.13,Default,9a,0,0,0,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:04.97,Default,All,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:24.24,Default,556,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.99,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,这样通往大裂隙{}的门扉就被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:34.16,Default,Head,0,0,0,,终于　人类解放之日近了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:38.04,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是被称作「比翼鸟」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.21,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种鸟只有一边的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:45.80,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不是雄性和雌性靠在一起行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:48.76,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就没办法飞上天　是一种不完全的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.55,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:51.55,Default,Z2,0,650,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:52.47,Default,16,650,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.27,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur5}却觉得这种生命的存在方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.14,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十分地美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:05.78,Default,9d,0,0,0,,呐　看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:09.78,Default,9e,0,0,0,,不会这么简单地结束么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:12.24,Default,9c,0,0,0,,核心复合体？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.08,Default,9b,0,0,0,,这也真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.87,Default,9a,0,0,0,,已经赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.79,Default,9a,0,0,0,,在这一带被碾碎前　我们先撤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.67,Default,16,0,0,0,,零贰　我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:22.29,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.01,Default,9a,0,0,0,,马上就有反应了么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.78,Default,56,0,0,0,,逃...逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.58,Default,196,0,0,0,,但是　那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:58.12,Default,15,0,0,0,,超大的手？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:58.97,Default-Top,9a,0,0,1,,剩下的我们会处理的　你们就在后面随便应付{摸摸鱼}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:05.95,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.29,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,第 6 次联合中队　准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.32,Default-Top,7,0,0,0,,目标 F2 地点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.45,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,确认到地下岩浆能量活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.19,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,重新测定振动波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.60,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,判定为「超雷曼级」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.67,Default-Top,8,0,0,0,,大裂隙{}会由爸爸们来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.84,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,要不要来做我的 Darling 呢{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.55,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,你很棒哦{ep02}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.34,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,很简单吧{ep03}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.96,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,你想乘上我？{ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.64,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,我可以带 Darling 你从这里离开{ep03}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.60,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,要放弃的话就趁现在哦{ep04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.72,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,当然是消灭怪物啊{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.52,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,其实你也觉得我是一个怪物吗?{ep04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.39,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,毕竟你只是我的饲料罢了{ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.73,Default-Top,Z2,0,0,0,,现在起你就是...{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.15,Default-Top,Z2,0,0,0,,我的 Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:25.83,Default-Top,Sign,0,0,0,,...千万不要离开我哦，Darling」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:29.91,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,そばに来て　崩れゆく抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:34.88,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ボクを怖がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:53.06,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,飛べない鳥が　夢見た空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:59.90,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,交わってく色　それは違う Red
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:08.12,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ドアを叩く音に　ボクは耳を塞いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:15.33,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,叩いてるのはキミ？それとも他の？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:21.30,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,Will your lips taste the kiss of death？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:28.89,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ダーリン運命が血管を走るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:35.98,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,動き始めた世界 ...愛？
