Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:49.83,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ボクを怖がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.66,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,Kiss me now
